# 12. In each year, how many movies have revenue smaller than the budget?

mv_norm[mv_norm["gross_margin"] < 0].groupby(by = ("year")).size()


# (esempio) interrogare il dataset: per l'anno 1970 quanti film hanno avuto un ricavo minore del budget (gross_margin < 0)? 

mv_norm[["title", "gross_margin"]][mv_norm["gross_margin"] < 0][mv_norm["year"] == "1970"]
